➜全身DNA断裂后，眼看着自己慢慢腐烂，这样的死法也太可怕了吧！
http://www.sohu.com/a/426719648_624188	10907
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201023/2fa05f2d41ec4e169ca38bf96375c9b4.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">作为一名合格的<strong>秃头骚年</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">掉一根头发</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你都能立马察觉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201023/490d0060b2aa447db2f4a56d45a23567.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>如果有一天</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>全身的DNA突然消失了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一瞬间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你又会有啥反应？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201023/62afe6bef67f40dd8a938fbaa2fe31e9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">在<strong>31.6亿</strong>个DNA消失那一瞬间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">由于<strong>细胞收缩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你感受到了一小股<strong>冲击波</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">会稍微抽搐一下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其次</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你的体重减少了<strong>150克</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个重量相当于</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你理了个发（长发及腰的发）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">或者</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你砍断了一根手指</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你感受一切如常</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>才</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>怪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>咧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">80天内</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你就会变成一副<strong>行走的尸体</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201023/0609092282404c30a12d50c98d72b054.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">凭什么死了150克DNA</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你就会成为一副行走的尸体？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这要先认识一下DNA</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201023/27b3b5d618a6434585b4e6e339879793.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201023/879d6526123f439eb9c46d64308bc94e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人体要维持正常吃喝拉撒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">少不了一样东西</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>蛋白质</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蛋白质是<strong>组成细胞的重要物质</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可是它种类多</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一个不小心生错了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那你就<strong>畸形</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要有座工厂指挥蛋白质生产</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这座工厂就是<strong>染色体</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它平时待在细胞核里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201023/938a4e34a5d54be09d0575d8735996e0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">工厂里有一本技术指南</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>DNA</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201023/224ee31cf43f4fb593209596e1307367.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">技术指南就跟老师划的期末重点一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">既有一堆屁话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也有一堆有用的话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这些有用的话<strong>记录着蛋白质的生产方法</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们称为<strong>基因</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>它是蛋白质生产的司令</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">每层梯子都编了个代码</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文本足足有<strong>3个Gb</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一旦梯子错了、乱了、断了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你也就畸形了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201023/5c7da610152d4f32adca2704880ddcf3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201023/860f8e14c24348d9b085ee4a0419184e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爱卿已经知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">DNA图书馆指导着蛋白质生成</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不同蛋白质会赋予细胞不同的功能</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>①遗传</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">3个Gb的DNA证明了你爸是你爸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">隔壁老王不是你爸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>②细胞轮班</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人体细胞要新陈代谢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>旧细胞死去，新细胞要及时轮班</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">作为蛋白质生产的司令</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">3个Gb的DNA指导着37万亿个细胞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">保证血液岗、免疫岗、肠胃岗等岗位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有新细胞<strong>按时打卡上班</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201023/95a2622f55e24a2b8e01c9fa79b3408d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一旦某段DNA咔嚓一下，断裂了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">某细胞也会咣当一下，停产</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比如白细胞停了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">病毒疯狂入侵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你就废了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">说到这里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你也就知道一小小小小段DNA丢失</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>后果有多渗人了吧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">幸好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">世界上还没出现全身DNA突然消失的病例</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201023/59112c1955c94cb581e3a07a57aec172.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201023/8b6a394b9f8746e4b68768446d98465e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">1999年，日本核燃料加工厂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">3名工人向沉淀槽中倒入了过量<strong>铀溶液</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">引发<strong>核裂变</strong>的临界事故</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那一瞬间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">3名工人都看到<strong>“蓝色荧光”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">死亡之光放出了巨量辐射</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201023/91eb324d023748c29617341956f10fcc.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">距离辐射源仅0.65米的<strong>大内久</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">遭受了16-23Gy的辐射量</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个量</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大约是普通人一年遭受的<strong>两万倍</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刚开始</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他像没事人一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自己走进医院，不用人抬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只是皮肤变黑了一点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">右手红肿了一点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201023/c90fcd9fcc5a4337bc543bba088a76d6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201023/527f9e1191ee40fbae0a5abd56b6d9da.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第二天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">体内的辐射线开始勐烈<strong>摧残染色体</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">原本排列有序的23对染色体</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有的断开几截</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有的黏在一起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201023/88cc52ba84e34cd1aa63acd6350b4428.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">染色体都<strong>严重变异</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">DNA更被<strong>砍断</strong>了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201023/d4706837bab4451ea8999007a9657045.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">DNA都断裂了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对蛋白质的指导生产工作自然也中断了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>没有新细胞的轮班</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>身体各种系统开始崩溃</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201023/47b8a584997947b9b786d55a56518a93.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">细胞代谢越快</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">受辐射攻击越快</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>皮肤</strong>代谢最快</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大内久皮肤迅速脱落</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">护士撕开他手上胶布</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都能撕下一层皮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为旧皮肤只能活3天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">缺了DNA的指导</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蛋白质合成失败</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">皮肤<strong>再也没长出新皮</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">化脓掉皮后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就露出了皮里的肌肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201023/e013ebd70f164ac4a03c1c1704cc1eb9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201023/c095590860b242a9b977d070399fc9aa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">接着<strong>肠道黏膜免疫系统</strong>崩溃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大内久一天腹泻3升</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此外，由DNA引导生产的<strong>酶</strong>也罢工了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没有酶分解蛋白质</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他连喝杯牛奶都会恶心拉稀</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">腹泻完开始拉血</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一天输10次血</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大量补血导致<strong>心脏</strong>跳动巨快</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>每分钟120次以上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">清醒感受着自己在腐烂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201023/ea52aaf7c92846d89653df5e4b3eba2e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201023/90fa7fd0f38141419af7347c580d7203.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大内久被病毒疯狂感染</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">抗菌队长<strong>白细胞</strong>能活3-12天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">趁着新白细胞没更新</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">病毒肆无忌惮</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>免疫系统</strong>全线瘫痪</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">止血队长<strong>血小板</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也只能活7-14天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没有新血小板轮班</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身体止不了血</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大内久肾脏衰竭也无法做手术</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肾脏还没修好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他可能就会失血过多而死了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201023/20090d49b4554412a64447e5a2fd44c4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201023/c0772496c0594185b56c8535fe4d9594.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">第83天晚上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>血液系统、免疫系统、各种器官罢工衰竭</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>病毒疯狂攻击，肉体急速腐烂</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大内久全身炭黑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">停止了呼吸</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201023/eea7491d229446008e37f542e4bc0840.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201023/49e8860eff02450ca175de0ce1c799a9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201023/900f353256974985b72f5f07fb05044e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">比身体腐烂更可怕的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你的神经系统、大脑、心脏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还在清醒工作着！！！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">感受着身体在慢慢腐烂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">直到变成一堆黑枯骨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这样的死亡方式也太惨了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201023/33c5ec95b1af4f0bba895098b2cfb405.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相比慢慢折磨而死</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">世界上最不知不觉的死亡方式</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">莫过于你站在了<strong>原子弹爆炸的爆心反应区</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">沐浴在原子弹上千万开尔的温度里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个温度连沙子都会瞬间变为玻璃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而你会瞬间被——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201023/299959b5918743e193954362660ae37e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个气化瞬间有多快呢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>少于0.1秒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而你从产生意识到作出反应</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">起码也得0.2秒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而那时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你早已成为宇宙的一颗尘埃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">哪里还会有反应</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">连一丝丝疼痛感都没有</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201023/9bc81d0cdf7b4c53ba53db6cf602c8c8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当然这种的方式</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你九成九是体验不到了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而其他方式不是痛就是丑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还是好好活着吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当条快乐的咸鱼难道不香吗！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201023/148d043480b04912b4acf55f081f70cb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
